        <p>
         Create a <a href="/signup">VIBEZ account</a>t! Once you have created a VIBEZ account, you can access the application and create a playlist. This playlist will be availabe to you when wifi is not available.  This allows you to VIBE ON when your "unplugged!
        </p>
      
